::Aerotaur::
       He shrugs.  "I honestly don't know.  All I know is that she is 
important, and that I must protect her.  Where she goes I go."  He glares 
firmly at Starstorm.  "Is that good enough?"  He doesn't wait for an answer 
but follows Flicker.
